{"tid":2259743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆喀什疫情反彈 164人染疫","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T05:41:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9308446cb5058316a02812ba64c860a0c212f0","tid":2259743,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/SB5VEVB3HZBA3B6RO6CSI6DHTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FSB5VEVB3HZBA3B6RO6CSI6DHTY%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=cb9788a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FSB5VEVB3HZBA3B6RO6CSI6DHTY%2F&h=7704d947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/SB5VEVB3HZBA3B6RO6CSI6DHTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新疆喀什疫情反彈 164人染疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/24O5p4UYWsCMuTs7BSg4M3Aw73I=/1920x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LMY5X437MVCY7CRSQUTPE347NU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F24O5p4UYWsCMuTs7BSg4M3Aw73I%3D%2F1920x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLMY5X437MVCY7CRSQUTPE347NU.jpg&h=7754191a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在疫情之下，喀什古城街道無人，商舖多數暫停營業。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n新疆喀什再次出現武漢肺炎疫情反彈情況，繼本月24日至25日共通報138名無症狀感染者後，昨日再新增26人，全部為25日確診個案的密切接觸者，三日累計164人確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或出現超級傳播者<br />\n<br />\n北京大學第一醫院呼吸和危重症醫學科主任王廣發表示，。。。。。。。。。，也不排除出現了「超級傳播者」。<br />\n<br />\n至於百多名感染者均為無症狀感染者，。。。。。。。。。。，可能有很多人會在隔離期間出現症狀。<br />\n<br />\n至於喀什民眾近期流向方面，。。。。。。。。。。。前十熱門遷出地，除新疆、青海和甘肅所屬地區外，僅有陝西西安上榜。<br />\n<br />\n環時網"},{"pid":"bfc314b07f3594280adcf754c166f1219712a4fa","tid":2259743,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"被感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a0587c2b720974dc96252cab5b26a12f2f3527","tid":2259743,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"支那缺水，新疆養唔起，<br />\n咪攞嚟造生化實驗場試毒"},{"pid":"022ecfc7f4a1cc44d1d00281a80ee571f2465400","tid":2259743,"uid":334720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n新疆呢D地型比較廣闊既地方 仲要比支那集中營咁控制住<br />\n都會爆百幾單出黎<br />\n<br />\n屌你其他支那省份無繼續爆發我都唔撚信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那幾時公開真實數據黎比大家參詳下, 睇下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係萬惡之源"},{"pid":"9b9315d11b68a15c1ec590b9371241ace88e4817","tid":2259743,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"到底支共刻意營造新彊同香港仍然染疫既原因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4947d0d5d15fe46be20113078e56ad494acca110","tid":2259743,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9315d11b68a15c1ec590b9371241ace88e4817","tid":2259743,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"到底支共刻意營造新彊同香港仍然染疫既原因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"人質外交<br />\n「東突人、香港人病緊，好需要我(支共)照顧。如果你地(外國) 打我，呢班人就會&rdquo;病死&rdquo;，問你地於心何忍?」<br />\n<br />\n和諧作用<br />\n「睇下東突香港班人唔聽黨話，結果就係受病折磨！」"},{"pid":"7dec7d5d2d1a29584854ab5f88ff706225cb7454","tid":2259743,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"呢個地區維族佔左9成以上"}]}